INSERT INTO kagzi.workflow_runs (
            run_id,
            external_id, task_queue, workflow_type, status,
            namespace, version, retry_policy, available_at,
            cron_expr, schedule_id
        )
        VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, 'PENDING', $5, $6, $7, NOW(), $8, $9)
        RETURNING run_id
